317
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:29,350
I don't know.

318
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:31,620
She has an account book, very thick.

319
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:34,460
The first page still records my dad's bride price.

320
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:37,180
People nowadays are all about writing blogs.

321
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:38,300
For their generation,

322
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:40,360
