Mr. Zhou!

383
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:43,120
What happened?

384
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:43,870
Make way, make way!

385
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:45,190
It's nothing, just a drill.

386
00:15:45,190 --> 00:15:46,110
Don't worry.

387
00:15:46,110 --> 00:15:47,310
We'll explain later.

388
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:47,960
Slowly.

389
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,000
A drill?

390
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,440
Are you tired?

391
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:54,510
