00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:56,370
Save your energy.

394
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,070
Actually, I'm fine.

395
00:15:57,070 --> 00:15:57,990
Let me tell you,

396
00:15:57,990 --> 00:15:59,590
before, I could carry a sofa on my head

397
00:15:59,590 --> 00:16:01,350
from the South Gate Market all the way back,

398
00:16:01,350 --> 00:16:01,870
