00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:11,300
What's wrong with you?

407
00:16:11,350 --> 00:16:12,070
What's wrong with you?

408
00:16:12,070 --> 00:16:13,110
Hurry up, go, go.

409
00:16:13,110 --> 00:16:14,290
Don't waste our time.

410
00:16:14,290 --> 00:16:15,720
What's wrong with my mom?

