421
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:29,000
It's fine. Hurry up and go home now.

422
00:16:32,210 --> 00:16:33,970
-Here, here.
-Okay.

423
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,960
My goodness.

424
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,920
Is your waist okay?

