00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,780
It takes at least three minutes to get here.

426
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:45,680
Then, adding the time to find a car and drive there,

427
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:48,940
it'll take another ten minutes or so to get to the hospital.

428
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:51,470
The key is the car. We have to have it ready at all times.

