00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:45,750
You don't need to worry.

522
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:46,510
I'm going to do my homework now.

523
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,390
Okay, okay.

524
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,710
See?

